Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,

Someone just signed in to your olubalance account from a new IP address.

  IP:      <%= @login_event.ip %>
  When:    <%= @login_event.created_at.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M %Z") %>
  Browser: <%= @login_event.user_agent %>

If this was you (new device, network, VPN), no action is needed.

If it wasn't you:
  - Change your password immediately.
  - Revoke trusted devices: https://olubalance.com/trusted_devices
  - Review recent activity: https://olubalance.com/security_events

— olubalance
